# IndiaMART LMS CRM Integration v2 - Project Overview

## Project Status
✅ **PRODUCTION READY** - Fully functional IndiaMART integration with AI quote management capabilities

## Key Features
- **IndiaMART API Integration**: Complete v2 API client with compliance
- **Rate Limiting**: 15-minute intervals, 5 calls/minute, 15-minute blocking
- **Error Handling**: Comprehensive error classification and retry logic
- **Date Formatting**: IST timezone support with DD-MON-YYYY and DD-MM-YYYYHH:MM:SS formats
- **Polling Service**: Automated lead fetching with Strategy 1 & 2
- **AI Integration**: Ready for quote management and lead scoring
- **AWS Ready**: Serverless architecture with DynamoDB, ElastiCache, Lambda, SageMaker

